nodes.text: The Kwymar sector was a sector located within the Outer Rim Territories. Planets in Kwymar included Doniphon, Kestos Minor, Picutorion, and Telos IV.
Wullf Yularen served in the Kwymar Sector Fleet over a decade before the Clone Wars. Ivor Drake represented Kwymar in the Galactic Senate during the Wars.
